{{BLP sources|date=March 2012}}
{{Wikify|date=March 2012}}
'''Al Amir Mohamed Waheed Deen''' is the current Vice President of the Republic of Maldives. He was appointed by President [[Mohamed Waheed Hassan]] on February 15, 2012, following the disputed resignation of the previous president, [[Mohamed Nasheed]]. He is also the Chairman of Bandos Island Resort. Deen is the son of Prince Abdullah Imaaduddeen and Koli Dhon Didi. He is also a member of the Maldivian Royal Family as his Grand father was Sultan Hajy Imaaduddeen IV.<ref>Haveeru News on 15th February 2012 , Maldives Royal Family Website </ref>

